Package: smoothemplik
Type: Package
Title: Smoothed Empirical Likelihood
Version: 0.0.11
Authors@R: person(given=c("Andreï", "Victorovitch"), family="Kostyrka",
        role=c("aut", "cre"), email="andrei.kostyrka@gmail.com")
Maintainer: Andreï V. Kostyrka <andrei.kostyrka@gmail.com>
Description: Smoothed Empirical Likelihood for asymtotically efficient
    estimation of conditional-moment-restriction-based models
    with focus on linear models under random sampling, variable-probability
    sampling, and with missing data in endogenous variables.
